{"tid":317574,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"而家d父母係咪變哂質","createTime":"2017-07-11T14:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T14:15:57.000Z","uid":40491,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"238fbdc382042c30b147a3892a36949da66a14b1","tid":317574,"uid":40491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"而家d父母真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說我搭緊地鐵個陣聽到有個細路係到唱是龜也是頭依首金曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁細路唔識野係到唱問題都不大<br />\n最大問題係佢不停唱，唱完廣東話就唱普通話<br />\n而佢隔離個個老母竟然可以為所不動，仲一路玩手機一路同個細路有講有笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌正常人就算唔介意個仔唱濕鳩歌，但係出到街見個仔on99到出哂面公開俾人笑都識得叫佢返屋企先唱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢知唔知其實d人唔係笑緊個細路而係笑鳩緊你唔撚識教仔咋傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終唔撚明d人生個仔出黎又唔撚教係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e80d3549b394e38ab8545238ba683a4ab8b6733","tid":317574,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"是龜頭也是賓周"},{"pid":"ff86308e010485f3de096932f3335b44f72e3346","tid":317574,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"都係一種方法"},{"pid":"998ac0f9c99ebbec0f5262c5251ce01edec777cb","tid":317574,"uid":40491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是龜頭也是賓周</blockquote><br />\n我諗依到個個都識唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係有冇人夠膽試下係老母面前唱下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d3065b4a1125a947f16097471d178fbcec0ea1","tid":317574,"uid":40491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係一種方法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"